Name: Fragmania.gg (BETA)
About the game: FragMania.GG is a third party matchmaking service (Currently in BETA) for Counter-Strike:Global Offensive. We offer: - 128 Tick Servers - 5v5 Ranked Matchmaking - Ladders - GOTV - Practice Servers (TDM etc) - Ladders - Advanced Statistics All accessible via our beta windows client. Our service is currently available in the following regions/areas: US-East US-Central US-West Europe Russia
